snippet.textDisplay:
Hi! I got a negative comment here, feel free to tell me your thoughts.


I think the song is very well made, it's good and it mostly sounds nice.
Of course, it's amazing how fast and still good he can rap, but I personally think that the lyrics are sometimes off-beat.
I love the Juice WRLD feature and it fits in aswell because he raps about how badass and sad he is.
Yes, it's very impressive that he topped "Rap god" but I think that the part at 2:45 sounds better than the part at 2:57 .
Here's why: I think 2x rap is good, you can definitely vibe to it and also understand most of the words.
But like 2:57 rap etc is way too fast, (which yes, is impressive of course) so I can't understand 1 word of it (which is the point of very fast rap, but still) and I can't like, nod my head or something to it if you understand. It's just not vibeable in my opinion.


What do you think? If you disagree, please tell me why and thank you so much for actually reading this :)
Have a good day!
snippet.textOriginal:
